3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20understand%20the%20roots%20of%20political%20violence%20in%20the%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20panchayat%20system%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20state%20became%20the%20first%20in%20the%20country%20to%20introduce%20a%20democratically%20elected%20three-tier%20panchayat%20system%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission.%20Prior%20to%20this%2C%20administration%20was%20mainly%20controlled%20by%20district%20magistrates%20and%20block%20development%20officers%2C%20with%20powerful%20wealthy%20families%20holding%20significant%20influence%20in%20respective%20regions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20panchayat%20system%20was%20a%20tool%20for%20the%20ruling%20Left%20Front%20to%20implement%20its%20land%20reforms%20policies%2C%20including%20land%20redistribution%20and%20securing%20tenancy%20rights%20for%20share-croppers.%20However%2C%20as%20land%20reforms%20began%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20%E2%80%98capturing%20territory%E2%80%99%20and%20power%20in%20villages%20through%20the%20panchayat%20system%20became%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Left%20Front%20government%20implemented%20direct%20elections%20for%20the%20three-tier%20panchayats%20under%20party%20symbols%2C%20thereby%20decentralising%20power%20and%20diminishing%20the%20influence%20of%20wealthy%20and%20influential%20families.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20transformation%20in%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20rural%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewir