%20Dwaipayan%20Bhattacharya%20termed%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%201990s%2C%20class%20dynamics%20gradually%20diminished%20and%20what%20remained%20was%20a%20struggle%20solely%20focused%20on%20retaining%20political%20power.%20Consequently%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecapturing%E2%80%99%20and%20control%20of%20panchayats%20grew%20into%20a%20strategic%20tool%20employed%20primarily%20to%20maintain%20political%20dominance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20decrease%20in%20agricultural%20income%20and%20a%20crippling%20lack%20of%20rural%20job%20opportunities%20in%20Bengal%2C%20panchayat%20polls%20have%20once%20again%20assumed%20a%20crucial%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Those%20in%20power%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%20can%20dictate%20job%20creation%2C%20income%20generation%2C%20and%20the%20mode%20of%20execution%20of%20government%20initiatives.%20Under%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20a%20direct%20flow%20of%20funds%20from%20central%20projects%20to%20rural%20bodies%2C%20bypassing%20the%20state%20government%2C%20was%20enabled.%20This%20approach%20gained%20further%20momentum%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%2C%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20continued%20to%20follow%20this%20course.%20As%20a%20consequence%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20funds%20allocated%20to%20the%20panchayats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Freport-15th-finance-commission-2021-26%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E15th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20West%20Bengal%20is%20projected%20to%20receive%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2017%2C199%20crore%20for%20rural%20development%20between%202021%20and%202026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20amount%20will%20mean%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20year%20for%20each%20of%20the%203%2C317%20panchayats%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20direct%20fund%20transfer%20schemes%20%E2%80%93%20which%20involve%20no%20intermediaries%20and%20direct%20crediting%20to%20a%20beneficiary%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20as%20in%20the%20MGNREGA%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20and%20for%20rural%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20panchayat%20structure%20is%20paramount.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20makes%20the%20panchayat%20it%20not%20just%20a%20political%20power%20centre%20but%20also%20one%20which%20holds%20considerable%20sway%20over%20the%20rural%20economy%2C%20directly%20affecting%20the%20lives%20of%20approximately%2070%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Controlling%20a%20panchayat%20allows%20a%20political%20party%20to%20influence%20land%20use%2C%20property%20rights%2C%20and%20resource%20allocation%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20creation%20of%20a%20beneficiary%20class%20who%20are%20expected%20to%20show%20loyalty.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConflicts%20and%20violence%20among%20political%20parties%20during%20the%20poll%20process%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20the%20competition%20to%20gain%20control%20over%20these%20valuable%20assets%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20also%20the%20rural%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689242277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-violence-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20state%20where%20access%20to%20political%20power%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20competition%20to%20secure%20it%20has%20grown%20particularly%20intense.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22c