nsider.com%2F64ae91868ed31300199e9387%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hamlet%20now%20has%20three%20operational%20g%C3%AEtes.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20need%20a%20property%20with%20at%20least%20two%20g%C3%AEtes%20to%20rent%20and%20two%20additional%20houses%3A%20one%20for%20our%20family%20and%20one%20for%20my%20mom%2C%20Helen%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Terry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20September%20we'd%20found%2010%20locations%20that%20met%20our%20requirements.%20Luckily%2C%20COVID-19%20travel%20restrictions%20had%20lifted%20that%20month%2C%20so%20we%20flew%20to%20France%20and%20visited%20several%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20we%20pulled%20up%20the%20drive%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lac-de-maison.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELac%20de%20Maison%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20three-acre%20farmstead%20in%20the%20peaceful%20countryside%20of%20the%20Poitou-Charentes%20region%2C%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222784%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20village%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae918d8ed31300199e9396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221476%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hamlet%20sprawls%20three%20acres%20of%20land.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20500-year-old%20hamlet%20comprised%20an%20owner's%20home%20and%20three%20operational%20g%C3%AEtes%2C%20with%20other%20derelict%20buildings%20on%20the%20site%20that%20could%20be%20renovated%20into%20additional%20g%C3%AEtes.%20It%20also%20had%20a%20beautiful%20garden%20with%20chickens%20and%20goats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20canceled%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20viewings%20and%20made%20an%20offer%20that%20day.%20We%20split%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20hamlet%20with%20my%20mom%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20were%20joining%20us.%20The%20hamlet%20cost%20430%2C000%20euros%20in%20total.%20We%20paid%20215%2C000%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20financed%20the%20purchase%20by%20selling%20our%20house%20in%20England.%20Any%20profits%20beyond%20the%20price%20of%20the%20property%20went%20toward%20renovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221326%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91888ed31300199e938b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20renovated%20old%20buildings%20into%20vacation%20rentals.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20we%20finalized%20the%20property%20purchase%20on%20December%2015%2C%202020%2C%20we%20didn't%20begin%20physically%20moving%20to%20France%20until%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20Brexit%20happened%2C%20changing%20all%20the%20rules%20and%20turning%20our%20move%20into%20a%20flurry%20of%20passports%20and%20spreadsheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20cost%20us%20around%206%2C000%20euros.%20But%20by%20the%20beginning%20of%202021%2C%20all%20six%20of%20us%20were%20in%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20renovated%202%20buildings%20while%20running%20the%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20family%20moved%20into%20the%20biggest%20g%C3%AEte%2C%20while%20Mom%20and%20Terry%20took%20the%20old%20owner's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20in%2C%20Mom%20and%20Terry%20realized%20that%20space%20wasn't%20suited%20to%20their%20purposes.%20And%20though%20we%20hadn't%20budgeted%20for%20it%20initially%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91948ed31300199e939f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20g%C3%AEtes%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20new%20bathroom%20became%20a%20complete%20overhaul%2C%20down%20to%20the%20bricks.%20Mom%20and%20Terry%20returned%20to%20the%20UK%20for%20about%20eight%20months%20while%20we%20completed%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saved%20money%20by%20doing%20any%20labor%20we%20could%20%E2%80%94%20plaster%2C%20floor%2C%20roofs%20%E2%80%94%20an%20experience%20with%20a%20learning%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20purchased%20the%20property%20knowing%20the%20previous%20owners%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20bookings%20for%20spring%20and%20five%20or%20six%20for%20the%20summer%2C%20including%20the%20g%C3%AEte%20we%20were%20living%20in.%20So%20when%20Mom%20and%20Terry%20left%2C%20we%20moved%20into%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20in%20that%20house%20until%20the%20construction%20was%20so%20extensive%20that%20we%20had%20to%20move%20into%20a%20camper%20on%20the%20property%20that%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae918c8ed31300199e9391%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20traditional%20French%20buildings%20date%20back%20500%20years.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20began%20hosting%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20experience%20either%20Dave%20or%20I%20had%20in%20hospitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20curve%20was%20steep%2C%20but%20since%20we%20both%20love%20people%20and%20had%20been%20on%20holiday%20before%2C%20we%20knew%20the%20kind%20of%20experience%20we%20wanted%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20advertising%20where%20French%20people%20look%20for%20their%20holidays%2C%20we%20generated%20enough%20bookings%20to%20stay%20afloat.%20We%20also%20decided%20to%20remain%20open%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20when%20the%20property%20had%20previously%20not%20been%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20was%20in%20preparation%20for%20renovating%20an%20old%20ruined%20barn%20into%20a%20four-bedroom%20g%C3%AEte%20and%20taking%20over%20one%20of%20the%20existing%20g%C3%AEtes%20as%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91838ed31300199e9381%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221010%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20inside%20on%20of%20the%20g%C3%AEtes.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20we%20braced%20ourselves%20for%20a%20loss%20of%20income%20as%20we%20took%20the%20large%20g%C3%AEte%20off%20the%20market%2C%20moved%20into%20it%2C%20and%20began%20construction%20on%20the%20ruin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20shell%20of%20a%20building%20had%20been%20empty%20for%20over%20100%20years%20%E2%80%94%20no%20rooms%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20and%20no%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222390%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91918ed31300199e9399%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20one%20of%20the%20g%C3%AEtes%20available%20to%20rent.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20with%20Mom%20and%20Terry's%20house%2C%20we%20did%20as%20much%20of%20the%20work%20as%20possible.%20We%20kept%20the%20original%20floors%2C%20and%20over%20nearly%2010%20months%20we%20turned%20everything%20around%20them%20into%20a%20new%20third%20g%C3%AEte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20exceeded%20our%2080%2C000%20euro%20budget%2C%20it's%20been%20worth%20the%20investment.%20Today%20all%20three%20g%C3%AEtes%20are%20fully%20occupied%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20from%20May%20through%20the%20beginning%20of%20September%20and%20every%20weekend%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222374%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91938ed31300199e939d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20one%20of%20the%20g%C3%AEtes%20available%20to%20rent.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20done%20renovating%20for%20now%2C%20but%20we%20continue%20to%20make%20minor%20tweaks%20to%20our%20residence%2C%20transforming%20it%20from%20a%20rental%20cottage%20into%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20in%20the%20countryside%20is%20wonderful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20old%20farmstead%20is%20so%20different%20from%20our%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20UK.%20Our%20nearest%20neighbors%20are%20a%20quarter-mile%2C%20not%20a%20doorstep%2C%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bigger%20village%20is%20just%20a%20bit%20down%20the%20road%20where%20the%20kids%20go%20to%20school.%20There's%20also%20a%20movie%20theater%2C%20a%20library%2C%20and%20a%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20have%20been%20in%20a%20French%20school%20since%20day%20one.%20For%20the%20first%20six%20months%20they%20despised%20us%2C%20the%20school%20%E2%80%94%20the%20whole%20enterprise.%20Two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20later%2C%20they're%20both%20thriving%20and%20fluent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221508%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae918a8ed31300199e938d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hamlet%20has%20lots%20of%20outdoor%20space%20and%20amenities.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDave%20and%20I%20were%20lucky%20to%20meet%20the%20wife%20of%20our%20builder%2C%20a%20lovely%20English-French%20lady%20who%20helped%20us%20navigate%20the%20French%20bureaucracy%20%E2%80%94%20what%20I%20found%20to%20be%20the%20most%20challenging%20part%20of%20this%20entire%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20you%20must%20fill%20out%20forms%20to%20reregister%20your%20child%20for%20the%20same%20school%2C%20with%20the%20same%20teacher%2C%20every%20year%2C%20even%20if%20nothing%20changes.%20I%20think%20it's%20just%20because%20the%20French%20like%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20a%2017th%20century%20French%20hamlet%20and%20holiday%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae91868ed31300199e9385%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22956%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20children's%20play%20area%20on%20the%20property.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Murphy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20B-and-B%20business%20allows%20us%20to%20live%20comfortably%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20move%20to%20France%20to%20make%20money.%20We%20know%20we'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20make%20as%20much%20here%20as%20we%20did%20with%20our%20big%20jobs%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20life%20is%20just%20better%20here.%20We%20can%20be%20there%20as%20our%20kids%20and%20my%20mom%20and%20Terry%20grow%20older.%20This%20business%20allows%20us%20to%20put%20family%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20essentially%20traded%20the%20value%20of%20our%20house%20in%20Manchester%20for%20Lac%20de%20Maison%2C%20and%20in%20the%20countryside%20your%20money%20goes%20so%20much%20further.%20We%20don't%20have%20to%20buy%20eggs%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20got%20them%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20knew%20that%20for%20the%20first%20two%20years%20we'd%20break%20e