ngs%20add%20to%20concerns%20on%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20AI-detection%20systems%20and%20systemic%20bias%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESystems%20that%20detect%20AI-generated%20writing%20are%20flagging%20essays%20written%20by%20non-native%20English%20speakers%20as%20bot-generated%2C%20researchers%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fpatterns%2Ffulltext%2FS2666-3899(23)00130-7%23%2520%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanford%20University%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20study%20published%20Monday%2C%20the%20researchers%20ran%20more%20than%20100%20essays%20written%20by%20non-native%20English%20speakers%20through%20seven%20popular%20GPT%20detectors.%20(GPT%20is%20the%20framework%20behind%20some%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%3Ewidely%20used%20chatbots%20today%2C%20including%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20The%20essays%20were%20written%20for%20an%20English-proficiency%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20also%20fed%20the%20detectors%20essays%20written%20by%20US%20eighth%20graders%20who%20speak%20English%20natively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20the%20essays%20written%20by%20non-native%20English%20speakers%20were%20marked%20as%20AI-generated%20by%20the%20detection%20systems%2C%20the%20Stanford%20researchers%20found.%20And%20one%20GPT-detection%20system%20flagged%20almost%2098%25%20of%20those%20essays%20as%20written%20by%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20evaluating%20essays%20written%20by%20eighth-grade%20native%20English%20speakers%2C%20the%20detection%20systems%20performed%20much%20better%2C%20assessing%20that%20about%2020%25%20of%20their%20essays%20were%20produced%20by%20AI.%20Still%20mislabeling%20human-written%20essays%20as%20bot-written%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20at%20the%20same%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20warned%20the%20discrepancy%20could%20cause%20considerable%20harm%20to%20non-native%20English%20speakers%20who%20could%20be%20falsely%20accused%20of%20submitting%20work%20produced%20by%20chatbots%20for%20school%20assignments%2C%20college%20applications%2C%20or%20for%20work%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-detection%20software%20is%20increasingly%20being%20marketed%20as%20a%20silver%20bullet%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-generated-tweets-study-openai-gpt3-misinformation-2023-6%5C%22%3Efloods%20of%20misinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20produced%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhisper-openai-dalle-2-ai-art-codex-who-owns-chatgpt-2023-3%5C%22%3Etools%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20Dall-E%20and%20MidJourney%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20study%20adds%20to%20the%20growing%20questions%20surrounding%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20these%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20and%20echoes%20longstanding%20calls%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-discrimination-bias-worse-problem-than-sentience-2022-6%5C%22%3Eaddress%20biases%20hardwired%20into%20AI%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatbots%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20generate%20written%20text%20by%20guessing%20the%20most%20logical%20word%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20follow%20in%20a%20sentence.%20It%20makes%20these%20guesses%20based%20on%20underlying%20large%20language%20models%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-cto-murati-wants-less-hype-around-gpt-4-chatgpt-2023-3%5C%22%3ELLMs%2C%20which%20are%20trained%20on%20datasets%3C%2Fa%3E%20comprised%20of%20mounds%20of%20data%20scraped%20from%20all%20sorts%20of%20publicly%20available%20sources%2C%20like%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20Wikipedia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20attributed%20the%20results%20of%20their%20study%20to%20a%20metric%20many%20GPT-detection%20systems%20use%20called%20%26quot%3Bt