led%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20flood%20barriers%20in%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20residential%20area%2C%20where%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20other%20top%20government%20officials%20reside%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20stem%20the%20surging%20river%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20floodwaters%20reached%20several%20key%20areas%20in%20Delhi%2C%20including%20the%20Secretariat%20housing%20the%20chief%20minister's%20office.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20universities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shutdown%20of%20all%20non-essential%20government%20offices%20in%20the%20city%20until%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20water%20level%20touched%20a%20record%20208.53%20meters%20at%2010%20am%2C%20surpassing%20a%2045-year-old%20record%2C%20the%20city%20scrambled%20to%20coordinate%20rescue%20and%20relief%20efforts.%20The%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20has%20termed%20the%20situation%20as%20%26quot%3Bextreme%26quot%3B%20and%20anticipates%20the%20water%20level%20to%20rise%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20public%2C%20has%20also%20advised%20private%20offices%20to%20adopt%20work-from-home%20arrangements%20until%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20these%20escalating%20challenges%2C%20Delhi%20is%20facing%20a%20drinking%20water%20shortage%20as%20three%20treatment%20plants%20have%20been%20flooded.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20addressed%20the%20issue%20on%20Twitter%2C%20stating%20that%20efforts%20will%20be%20made%20to%20restore%20the%20plants%20as%20soon%20as%20Yamuna%20water%20recedes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20floodwaters%20entering%20the%20city%2C%20areas%20such%20as%20the%20Boat%20Club%2C%20Pandav%20Nagar%2C%20Gandhi%20Nagar%2C%20and%20Bhajanpura%2C%20among%20others%2C%20were%20inundated.%20The%20Delhi%20Secretariat%2C%20which%20houses%20the%20offices%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20cabinet%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20bureaucrats%2C%20was%20also%20affected%20by%20the%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraffic%20movement%20has%20been%20severely%20impaired.%20The%20traffic%20police%20have%20issued%20advisories%20about%20restrictions%20and%20regulations%20on%20vehicular%20movement%20due%20to%20the%20rising%20water%20levels%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20River.%20Commercial%20vehicles%20not%20headed%20for%20Delhi%20have%20been%20told%20not%20to%20enter%20the%20city%20and%20are%20being%20diverted%20to%20the%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20Peripheral%20Expressways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20centre%20for%20intervention%20as%20the%20situation%20deteriorates.%20To%20maintain%20order%2C%20city%20police%20have%20banned%20gatherings%20of%20four%20or%20more%20people%20and%20public%20movement%20in%20groups%20in%20flood-prone%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(DDMA)%2C%20led%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20meet%20to%20discuss%20and%20manage%20the%20flood%20situation%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689236220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fl07l9nq_kejriwal-house-delhi-flood-ndtv_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ffloodwater-now-350-m-away-from-arvind-kejriwals-home-4203189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20flood%20crisis%2C%20reaching%20a%20level%20unseen%20in%2045%20years%2C%20has%20also%20led%20to%20the%20imposition%20of%20flood%20barriers%20in%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20residential%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ffloodwater-now-350-m-away-from-arvind-kejriwals-home-4203189%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ffloodwater-now-350-m-away-from-arvind-kejriwals-home-4203189%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ffloodwater-now-350-m-away-from-arvind-kejriwals-home-4203189%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Slams%20UP%20Govt%2C%20Says%20It%20Has%20%E2%80%98Scant%20Respect%E2%80%99%20for%20Orders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20over%20non%20compliance%20with%20the%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Futtar-pradesh-government-officials-condemned-by-supreme-court-for-disregarding-orders-on-convict-remission-delay-101689189475802.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20UP%20government%20officials%20have%20%E2%80%9Cscant%20respect%E2%80%9D%20for%20orders%20while%20condemning%20the%20year-long%20delay%20in%20deciding%20the%20matter%20of%20remission%20for%20convicts%20serving%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20above%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20remarked%20when%20the%20state%20government%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20binding%20the%20governor%20%E2%80%93%20the%20constitutional%20authority%20required%20to%20take%20the%20final%20decision%20after%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20on%20remission%20pleas%20%E2%80%93%20to%20a%20court-mandated%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhosoever%20it%20may%20be%2C%20nobody%20is%20above%20the%20law.%20There%20are%20people%20who%20have%20been%20languishing%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%20Our%20direction%20was%20passed%20in%20May%202022%20to%20decide%20applications%20of%20the%20petitioners%20before%20us%20within%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%2C%20which%20also%20included%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Datta%2C%20told%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20additional%20advocate%20general%2C%20Ardhendumauli%20Kumar%20Prasad%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20directed%20the%20state%20home%20department%E2%80%99s%20principal%20secretary%20to%20remain%20present%20in%20the%20court%20on%20August%2029%20if%20the%20authorities%20fail%20to%20dispose%20of%20all%20pending%20applications%20within%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20livid%20that%20the%20UP%20government%20was%20yet%20to%20act%20on%20its%20direction%2C%20given%20on%20May%2016%2C%202022%2C%20asking%20the%20authorities%20to%20take%20a%20final%20call%20within%20three%20months.%20In%20its%20May%202022%20order%2C%20the%20court%20had%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20the%20petitioners%2C%20lodged%20in%20Bareilly%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Jail%2C%20had%20completed%20more%20than%2014%20years%20of%20their%20actual%20sentence%20without%20remission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20remission%20policy%20along%20with%20several%20directives%20passed%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20obligate%20the%20state%20government%20to%20dispose%20off%20a%20prisoners%20remission%20plea%20within%20three%20months%20of%20it%20becoming%20eligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20disrespect%20your%20authorities%20are%20showing%2C%20we%20think%20we%20will%20have%20to%20take%20some%20harsh%20steps.%20Your%20officers%20have%20scant%20respect%20for%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20court.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20your%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2042%20convicts%20who%20had%20approached%20the%20top%20court%20last%20year%2C%20several%20were%20released%20or%20acquitted%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20pending%20decisions%20on%20their%20remission%20pleas%2C%20and%20at%20least%20seven%20such%20applications%20for%20premature%20release%20were%20still%20pending%20before%20a%20government%20authority%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689236146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F17134928%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_01-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-slams-up-govt-says-it-has-scant-respect-for-orders%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20UP%20government%20for%20not%20acting%20on%20the%20court's%20direction%20on%20remission%20pleas%20from%20May%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-slams-up-govt-says-it-has-scant-respect-for-orders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Case%20Registered%20Against%20Meitei%20Leepun%20Chief%20for%20'Promoting%20Enmity'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13132622%2FKT-6-June.01_15_29_19.Still003.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Based%20on%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20a%20Kuki%20students%E2%80%99%20group%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Pramot%20Singh%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Meitei%20Leepun%20group%20that%20is%20accused%20of%20instigating%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20for%20promoting%20enmity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-police-file-case-against-meitei-leepun-chief-pramot-singh%2Farticle67072757.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20(KSO)%20on%20June%2013%20but%20the%20case%20was%20registered%20only%20on%20July%208%20at%20the%20Kangpokpi%20police%20station.%20The%20first%20inf