%20good%20role%20in%20it.%20It%20was%20just%20unfortunate%2C%20it%20didn't%20pan%20out.%20The%20first%20day%20just%20left%20us%20too%20much%20behind%20in%20the%20shed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I'd%20like%20to%20give%20to%20my%20teammates%20and%20Indian%20cricket%20as%20a%20whole%20is%20some%20understanding%20and%20my%20best%20efforts%20on%20the%20field%20and%20I'd%20like%20to%20leave%20it%20at%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20about%20wickets%20or%20runs%2C%20it%20is%20about%20the%20memories%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20is%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20powers%2014%20years%20into%20international%20cricket%20but%2C%20looking%20back%2C%20he%20is%20amazed%20how%20the%20time%20has%20flown%20by.%20He%20is%20at%20a%20stage%20where%20making%20memories%20is%20more%20important%20than%20getting%20wickets%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20literally%2014%20years%20on%20the%20go%20and%20if%20you%20include%20IPL%20also%2C%20it's%20been%20almost%20a%2015-16%20years%20journey.%20It's%20just%20gone%20like%20that.%20All%20I%20would%20tell%20anybody%20is...%20the%20first%20time%20I%20met%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20coach%2C%20he%20made%20this%20statement%3A%20'It's%20not%20about%20how%20many%20wickets%20you%20take%2C%20how%20many%20runs%20you%20score.%20You'll%20forget%20about%20all%20of%20them.%20It%20is%20only%20the%20great%20memories%20you%20create%20as%20a%20team%20that'll%20stick%20with%20you.'%20%26quot%3BI'm%20totally%20behind%20that.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20he's%20brainwashed%20me%20to%20do%20that.%20From%20my%20point%20of%20view%2C%20I%20definitely%20think%20that%20this%20journey%20has%20gone%20so%20fast%20that%20I'm%20not%20even%20able%20to%20recollect%20what%20has%20happened%2C%20and%20how%20it%20has%20gone%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20gratitude%20and%20I'm%20very%20grateful%20for%20the%20journey%20and%20what%20the%20game%20has%20given%20to%20me.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20more%20such%20moments%20will%20come%20to%20me%2C%20but%20whatever%20comes%20my%20way%2C%20I'll%20try%20to%20enjoy%20it%20completely.%26quot%3B%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20also%20changed%20his%20outlook%20towards%20life%20and%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Covid%20when%20cricket%20began%20again%2C%20I%20promised%20myself%20that%20I'll%20enjoy%20whatever%20happens...%20whether%20I'm%20playing%2C%20getting%20dropped%20or%20if%20I'm%20retiring.%20Whatever%20happens%2C%20I%20will%20enjoy%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnjoyed%20the%20bounce%20on%20offer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20who%20was%20introduced%20into%20the%20attack%20as%20early%20as%20the%20ninth%20over%2C%20made%20full%20use%20of%20the%20bounce%20on%20offer%20at%20Windsor%20Park.%20The%20West%20Indies%20batters%20offered%20little%20resistance%20and%20Ashwin%20was%20too%20good%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20bounce%20from%20the%20wicket%2C%20especially%20from%20the%20pavilion%20end.%20The%20wicket%20had%20some%20slope%20also%20which%20gave%20us%20bounce.%20But%20we%20utilised%20the%20first%20session%20very%20well.%20The%20wicket%20had%20some%20moisture%20and%20it%20was%20coming%20off%20it%20very%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20saw%2C%20they%20showed%20a%20graphic%20that%20it%20was%20turning%20more%20(in%20the%20second%20session)%2C%20but%20the%20turn%20was%20very%20slow.%20But%20in%20the%20first%20session%2C%20there%20was%20bounce%2C%20and%20pace%20off%20was%20good%2C%20there%20was%20bite.%20We%20utilised%20it%20very%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp