f%20the%20iconic%20Park%20Street%20(Kolkata)%20lies%20a%20culinary%20gem%20that%20has%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%3A%20Peter%20Cat.%20With%20a%20rich%20history%20and%20a%20reputation%20that%20precedes%20it%2C%20this%20establishment%20has%20secured%20its%20place%20among%20Taste%20Atlas's%20150%20most%20legendary%20restaurants%20in%20the%20world%2C%20ranking%20at%20an%20impressive%2017th%20position.%20Among%20the%20handful%20of%20Indian%20restaurants%20featured%20on%20this%20list%2C%20Peter%20Cat%20has%20always%20been%20a%20cherished%20favourite%20among%20locals%20and%20tourists%2C%20alike.%20Intrigued%20by%20its%20acclaim%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20restaurant%20to%20uncover%20the%20secrets%20behind%20its%20allure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EFood%20That%20Brought%20Fame%20To%20Peter%20Cat%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20fellow%20diners%2C%20it%20became%20evident%20that%20while%20sizzlers%20are%20a%20popular%20option%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Chelo%20Kebab%20that%20reigns%20as%20the%20star%20dish%20of%20the%20restaurant.%20Taste%20Atlas%20too%20mentioned%20it%20as%20the%20must-try%20dish%20in%20the%20restaurant.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ELet's%20Learn%20More%20About%20Chelo%20Kebab...%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chelo%20Kebab%20is%20a%20potpourri%20of%20flavours%2C%20a%20culinary%20creation%20that%20has%20rightly%20earned%20its%20place%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20patrons.%20Picture%20a%20bed%20of%20buttered%20rice%2C%20its%20grains%20perfectly%20cooked%20and%20fragrant%2C%20topped%20with%20lightly%20grilled%20tomatoes%20and%20a%20medley%20of%20vegetables.%20Served%20along%20with%20seekh%20kebabs%20and%20chicken%20kebabs%20on%20the%20side%2C%20the%20succulence%20of%20the%20kebabs%20and%20the%20charred%20aroma%20of%20the%20vegetables%20was%20enough%20to%20entice%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriosity%20led%20us%20to%20engage%20with%20other%20visitors%20to%20the%20restaurant.%20We%20asked%20one%20of%20them%20what%20is%20so%20special%20about%20Chelo%20Kebab.%20She%20surprised%20us%20by%20revealing%20that%20she%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20figure%20that%20out%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Despite%20countless%20visits%2C%20the%20secret%20behind%20its%20popularity%20still%20remains%20a%20mystery!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Ffood-drinks%2Fkolkata-food-trail-7-places-you-must-visit-to-experience-the-citys-food-palate-3775981%5C%22%3EKolkata%20Food%20Trail%3A%207%20Places%20You%20Must%20Visit%20To%20Experience%20The%20City's%20Food%20Palate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3ENostalgia%20And%20Memories%20-%20Peter%20Cat%20Serves%20As%20A%20Remembrance%20Of%20Good%20Times%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20shared%20nostalgic%20tales%20of%20their%20cherished%20memories%20at%20Peter%20Cat%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20their%20childhood.%20The%20establishment's%20impeccable%20hospitality%20and%20commitment%20to%20delivering%20high-quality%20cuisine%20have%20left%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20their%20hearts.%20Year%20after%20year%2C%20Peter%20Cat%20has%20continued%20to%20astound%20its%20patrons%20with%20its%20culinary%20excellence%2C%20ensuring%20that%20each%20visit%20is%20an%20unforgettable%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20just%20the%20food%20at%20Peter%20Cat%2C%20we%20marvelled%20at%20the%20timeless%20ambience.%20The%20walls%20told%20stories%20of%20generations%20past%2C%20while%20the%20aroma%20of%20spices%20created%20an%20atmosphere%20that%20is%20both%20inviting%20and%20comforting.%20It%20is%20no%20wonder%20that%20Peter%20Cat%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Kolkata's%20food%20culture%2C%20now%20putting%20the%20city%20on%20the%20global%20culinary%20map.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689231540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7aq8ub4g_peter-cat-kolkata_640x480_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.nd