y%20Council%20epitomised%20the%20dissonance%20of%20an%20institution%20not%20in%20step%20with%20a%20changed%20world%20order%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIts%20skewed%20membership%20leads%20to%20opaque%20decision%20making%20processes%2C%20which%20adds%20to%20its%20helplessness%20in%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20today.%20I%20think%20most%20countries%20are%20clear%20on%20what%20changes%20they%20would%20like%20to%20see%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%2C%20including%20on%20the%20role%20India%20should%20play.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20shared%20the%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20the%20French%20media%20at%20his%20official%20residence%20in%20Delhi%2C%20before%20flying%20today%20to%20France%2C%20where%20he%20will%20be%20the%20guest%20of%20honour%20at%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20celebrations%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%20with%20unparalleled%20social%20and%20economic%20diversity%2C%20our%20success%20will%20demonstrate%20that%20democracy%20delivers.%20That%20it%20is%20possible%20for%20harmony%20to%20exist%20amidst%20diversity.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20is%20a%20natural%20expectation%20of%20adjustments%20in%20the%20international%20system%20and%20institutions%20to%20give%20the%20rightful%20place%20to%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20emphasised%20on%20India's%20role%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20the%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rights%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20have%20been%20long%20denied.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20is%20a%20feeling%20of%20anguish%20among%20the%20members%20of%20Global%20South%2C%20that%20they%20are%20forced%20into%20undertaking%20action%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20decision%20making%20they%20don't%20find%20a%20place%20or%20voice%20for%20themselves.%20The%20true%20spirit%20of%20democracy%20has%20not%20been%20respected%20vis-a-vis%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20elaborated%20on%20his%20oft-quoted%20comment%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20that%20today%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20must%20ned%2C%20he%20said%2C%20expressing%20deep%20concern%20about%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20stand%20has%20been%20clear%2C%20transparent%20and%20consistent.%20I%20have%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%20We%20have%20urged%20both%20sides%20to%20resolve%20issues%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%20I%20told%20them%20that%20India%20is%20ready%20to%20support%20all%20genuine%20efforts%20that%20can%20help%20bring%20this%20conflict%20to%20an%20end.%20We%20believe%20that%20all%20countries%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20respect%20the%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20to%20abide%20by%20international%20law%20and%20adhere%20to%20the%20UN%20Charter%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20soft%20power%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20exports%20have%20never%20been%20war%20and%20subjugation%2C%20but%20yoga%2C%20ayurveda%2C%20spirituality%2C%20science%2C%20mathematics%2C%20and%20Astronomy.%20We%20have%20always%20been%20a%20contributor%20to%20global%20peace%20and%20progress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20world%20makes%20progress%20only%20when%20it%20learns%20to%20let%20go%20of%20anachronistic%20and%20outdated%20notions%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20considered%20%26quot%3Bwestern%20values%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20universal%20or%20whether%20other%20countries%20should%20find%20their%20own%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689230100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim