is%20voice%20note%2C%20Popov%20said%20he%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20choice%20of%20either%20telling%20his%20bosses%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20hear%20or%20to%20%26quot%3Bcall%20a%20spade%20a%20spade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPopov%20said%20he%20decided%20to%20question%20the%20Kremlin%20over%20Russia's%20lack%20of%20counter-battery%20combat%20capabilities%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20artillery%20reconnaissance%20stations%2C%20and%20the%20mass%20Russian%20casualties%20that%20have%20resulted%20from%20this%20shortfall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20urged%20his%20superiors%20to%20rotate%20troops%20and%20relieve%20those%20who%20had%20fought%20on%20the%20frontlines%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Popov%2C%20he%20was%20immediately%20fired%20from%20his%20post%20by%20Russia's%20top%20general%2C%20Valery%20Gerasimov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20commanders%20of%20divisional%20regiments%20said%20today%2C%20the%20servicemen%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20of%20Ukraine%20could%20not%20break%20through%20our%20army%20from%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20Popov%20said%20in%20his%20voice%20note%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Feurope%2Flive-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-news-07-12-23%2Fh_bd7f938de72999bfbc3ab485fe88279c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20translation%20by%20CNN.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BOur%20senior%20commander%20hit%20us%20from%20the%20rear%2C%20treacherously%20and%20vilely%20decapitating%20the%20army%20at%20the%20most%20difficult%20and%20tense%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20neither%20the%20Russian%20state%20media%20nor%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20has%20commented%20on%20Popov's%20remarks%2C%20whether%20he%20has%20been%20fired%2C%20or%20on%20the%20circumstances%20of%20such%20a%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Defense%20Ministry%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20