only%20yield%20about%201.5%20to%202%20crore%20boxes%20as%20opposed%20to%203.36%20crore%20boxes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20significant%20drop%20in%20production%20is%20bound%20to%20directly%20affect%20the%20income%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20rural%20households.%20To%20comprehend%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20we%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20through%20rain-affected%20Himachal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20first%20stop%20was%20in%20the%20Banjar%20Valley%2C%20the%20region%20that%20pioneered%20apple%20cultivation.%20The%20changing%20climate%20has%20posed%20significant%20challenges%20here.%20Apple%20cultivation%20has%20now%20shifted%20to%20higher%20elevations.%20We%20climbed%20the%20mountainside%20near%20Bhattar%20and%20reached%20the%20last%20village%2C%20Gadincha%2C%20where%20we%20spoke%20with%20Ramdass%2C%20a%20young%20apple%20farmer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20year%20has%20been%20a%20complete%20loss.%20Heavy%20landslides%20have%20destroyed%20apple%20trees%20and%20local%20wheat%20harvests.%20It%20all%20began%20with%20erratic%20weather%20in%20March-April%20when%20the%20pink%20buds%20were%20blooming.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20temperatures%20dropped%20to%20zero%2C%20turning%20the%20pink%20buds%20black.%20Lack%20of%20sunlight%20for%20a%20few%20days%20led%20to%20a%2010-15%25%20loss%20in%20flowering.%20Subsequently%2C%20weather%20fluctuations%2C%20erratic%20rain%20and%20hail%20storms%20affected%20the%20remaining%20flowering%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20total%20loss%20of%20about%2040%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramdass%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20hopes%20for%20a%20harvest%2C%20Ramdass%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20situated%20in%20the%20high%20mountains%2C%20September%20is%20the%20harvest%20time.%20This%20year%2C%20I%20may%20only%20get%2010-15%20crates%20compared%20to%20the%20regular%20season%E2%80%99s%20500-600%20crates%20on%20my%20four%20bighas.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20recover%20the%20input%20costs%20this%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20descended%2C%20we%20witnessed%20the%20devastation%20caused%20by%20the%20rains.%20Wheat%20and%20pea%20fields%20were%20destroyed%2C%20old%20bridges%20had%20been%20swept%20away%2C%20mountain%20trails%20eroded%2C%20and%20the%20rivers%20and%20rivulets%20flowed%20violently%20down%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fclimate-change-women-of-colour-impact%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EHow%20Climate%20Change%20Impacts%20Women%20of%20Colour%20Across%20the%20Globe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20north%20into%20the%20deeper%20parts%20of%20the%20Kullu%20valley%2C%20we%20trekked%20up%20to%20Nathan%20village%2C%20situated%20in%20the%20high%20mountains.%20The%20road%20was%20mostly%20washed%20out%2C%20and%20the%20village%20lacked%20electricity%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20total%20blackout.%20Here%2C%20we%20met%20Pali%20Thakur%2C%20another%20young%20apple%20farmer%2C%20who%20was%20filled%20with%20despair.%20We%20walked%20through%20his%20apple%20orchard%20which%20was%20devoid%20of%20flowers%20and%20battered%20by%20the%20rain.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20plant%2025%20trees%20per%20bigha%2C%20and%20as%20you%20can%20see%2C%20none%20of%20them%20have%20good%20fruits%20or%20flowers.%20The%20rain%20and%20hail%20have%20caused%20extensive%20damage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIntrigued%20by%20the%20actual%20losses%2C%20I%20inquired%20further.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Nathan%2C%20being%20situated%20on%20a%20higher%20mountain%2C%20we%20already%20spend%20more%20on%20labor%20and%20transportation.%20However%2C%20we%20calculate%20costs%20per%2020%20kg%20apple%20box%20overall.%20We%20spend%20Rs%2090%20for%20transport%20and%20packing%2C%20Rs%2028%20on%20fertilisers%2C%20Rs%2020%20on%20pesticides%20and%20sprays%20and%20Rs%2020%20on%20weeding.%20So%2C%20approximately%20Rs%20210-250%20per%20crate%20accounts%20for%20the%20input%20costs%20each%20season.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20factored%20in%20the%20land%20value%2C%20family%20labor%2C%20and%20other%20expenses.%20Since%20we%20only%20have%20one%20crop%20per%20year%2C%20our%20entire%20earnings%20depend%20on%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pali%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPali%2C%20like%20most%20farmers%20in%20his%20village%2C%20did%20not%20anticipate%20a%20good%20harvest.%20However%2C%20the%20challenges%20extend%20beyond%20the%20Kullu%20valley.%20Heading%20towards%20Shimla%2C%20I%20met%20R.S.%20Minhas%2C%20who%20oversees%20a%20cluster-based%20business%20organisation%20working%20with%20over%2040%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOS)%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20focus%20of%20our%20discussion%20was%20the%20apple%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CApple%20production%20is%20significantly%20lower%20this%20year.%20Flowering%20was%20affected%20not%20only%20in%20Shimla%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20but%20also%20throughout%20Himachal.%20The%20pollen%20failed%20to%20mature%20due%20to%20temperature%20variations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20understand%20the%20underlying%20causes%2C%20I%20delved%20into%20the%20basics%20of%20apple%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CApple%20has%20three%20flowering%20stages%2C%20and%20two%20of%20these%20stages%20were%20adversely%20affected%20not%20only%20in%20Shimla%20and%20surrounding%20areas%20but%20across%20Himachal.%20Excessive%20cold%20followed%20by%20heat%20led%20to%20the%20withering%20of%20apple%20flowers.%20Some%20lucky%20farmers%20witnessed%20only%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20flowering.%20Overall%2C%20apple%20harvests%20are%20in%20a%20dire%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Minhas%20elaborated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fapple-growers-bjp-polls-himachal-pradesh%5C%22%3EIn%20Poll-Bound%20Himachal%2C%20Disgruntled%20Apple%20Growers%20May%20Be%20a%20Stumbling%20Block%20for%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReturning%20to%20Delhi%20I%20stopped%20at%20the%20Azadpur%20Mandi%20to%20answer%20one%20burning%20question%3A%20How%20would%20the%20market%20respond%20to%20this%20situation%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spoke%20with%20Amitabh%20Dhavan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20traders%20at%20Azadpur%20Mandi%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20who%20represents%20JCO%20traders.%20He%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CProduction%20is%20significantly%20lower%2C%20around%2050%25%20to%2040%25%20less%2C%20and%20apple%20prices%20will%20rise%20by%20approximately%2025%25%20this%20year.%20Apart%20from%20the%20impact%20on%20Himachal%20and%20Kashmiri%20apples%2C%2099%25%20of%20the%20cold%20storage%20apples%20have%20also%20been%20depleted.%20The%20only%20remaining%20option%20is%20imported%20apples%2C%20which%20will%20be%20sold%20at%20a%20premium%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20Dhavan%20attributed%20the%20situation%20to%20one%20factor%20%E2%80%93%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20undoubtedly%20the%20weather%2C%20100%25.%20Global%20warming%20and%20climate%20change%20have%20caused%20erratic%20weather%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Can%20you%20believe%20it%20snowed%20in%20Lahaul%20and%20Spiti%20recently%3F%20There%20was%20an%20extended%20winter%2C%20followed%20by%20sudden%20rains%20and%20heatwaves.%20Apple%20trees%20have%20been%20affected%20from%20Rajgarh%20to%20Lahaul%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApple%E2%80%99s%20fate%20is%20sealed%20by%20climate%20change%20this%20year.%20It%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20forbidden%20fruit%2C%20but%20it%C2%A0%20will%20undoubtedly%20be%20the%20most%20expensive%20fruit%20this%20season%20.%20And%20the%20money%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20tweets%20at%20%40Indrassingh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689220754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13090033%2F3777642918_8b937f9b6e_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimachal-climate-change-apple-production-prices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%E2%80%99s%20fate%20is%20sealed%20by%20climate%20change%20this%20year.%20It%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20forbidden%20fruit%2C%20but%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20be%20the%20most%20expensive%20fruit%20this%20season.%20And%20the%20money%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20farmers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimachal-climate-change-apple-production-prices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pita%20Limjaroenrat%3A%20Thailand's%20reformist%20leader%20faces%20uncertain%20PM%20vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689220752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FC70B%2Fproduction%2F_130355905_d281b278574506ee67e1a01b9a353adcdb69d667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66172289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20who%20won%20the%20election%20must%20overcome%20conservative%20rivals%20and%20last-ditch%20legal%20hurdles%20to%20take%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A86%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66172289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66172289.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66172289.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Jong%20Un%