%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98voiceless%E2%80%99.%20At%20rallies%2C%20he%20was%20frequently%20taunted%20as%20%E2%80%98Maun%E2%80%99mohan%20Singh%2C%20playing%20on%20the%20Hindi%20word%20for%20silence.%20At%20a%20Shimla%20rally%2C%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnarendra-modi-mocks-pm-with-maunmohan-singh-503033%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20why%20%E2%80%98Maunmohan%E2%80%99%20Singh%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20kept%20a%20stony%20silence%20on%20issues%20like%20inflation%20and%20price%20rise%20under%20the%20UPA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20epithet%20Modi%20threw%20at%20Manmohan%20Singh%20is%20now%20rebounding%20on%20him%20with%20a%20vengeance.%20Some%20call%20it%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20own%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ekarma%20while%20others%20say%20it%20is%20Keshubhai%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20curse%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20in%202012%2C%20Modi%20found%20himself%20isolated.%20Even%20the%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Frss-pulls-up-modi-for-forcing-gadkaris-hand%2Farticle3484272.ece%5C%22%3Eorgan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPanchjanya%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20hit%20out%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98style%20of%20functioning%E2%80%99%20as%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPitted%20against%20Modi%20were%20an%20array%20of%20Gujarat%20seniors%20like%20former%20chief%20minister%20Suresh%20Mehta%2C%20Kashiram%20Rana%2C%20Gordhan%20Zadaphia%2C%20Nalin%20Bhat%2C%20Sidharth%20Parmar%20and%20Pravin%20Maniar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAging%20and%20ailing%2C%20Keshubhai%20Patel%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fkeshubhai-patel-continues-his-tirade-against-narendra-modi%2Farticleshow%2F15034271.cms%5C%22%3Ecursed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20old%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E