ster%20should%20come%20to%20the%20house%20to%20explain%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20Adanis.%20While%20Modi%20himself%20maintained%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emaun%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%20along%2C%20his%20colleagues%20persistently%20stonewalled%20every%20demand%20for%20public%20scrutiny%2C%20made%20in%20and%20outside%20parliament.%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20alleging%20that%20the%20money%20involved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fadani-is-merely-a-front-for-modi-kejriwal%2Farticle66673157.ece%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98actually%E2%80%99%20belonged%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20Adani%20was%20merely%20a%20front%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20an%20extremely%20serious%20allegation%20levelled%20by%20a%20chief%20minister.%20He%20has%20challenged%20the%20very%20personal%20integrity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister.%20Modi%20had%20in%20the%20past%20charged%20the%20UPA%20government%20with%20a%20series%20of%20scams.%20But%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20accused%20Manmohan%20Singh%20of%20personal%20involvement.%20In%20fact%2C%20no%20prime%20minister%20in%20India%20was%20ever%20accused%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20direct%20personal%20involvement%20in%20any%20such%20misdemeanours%2C%20not%20even%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20enriching%20his%20friends%20but%20not%20himself.%20This%20renders%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20Adani%20imbroglio%20even%20more%20surprising.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07213949%2FScreenshot-2023-02-07-at-9.38.38-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22