rubbing%20shoulders%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20party%20bosses%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20the%20police%20were%20manhandling%20the%20wrestlers%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20detained%20and%20kept%20in%20the%20police%20station%20for%20hours%20before%20finally%20being%20charged%20with%20rioting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20one%20stage%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20were%20so%20disheartened%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20break%20his%20silence%20that%20they%20went%20to%20Hardwar%20to%20throw%20their%20medals%20into%20the%20Ganga.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20persuaded%20not%20to%20do%20so%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions.%20The%20wrestlers%20also%20got%20widespread%20support%20from%20the%20middle%20classes%20and%20youth.%20A%20C-Voter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Fmost-indians-want-brij-bhushan-arrested-expect-pm-modi-to-intervene-survey%2F3115464%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2068.4%25%20of%20the%20people%20interviewed%20wanted%20the%20PM%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20the%20accused%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhap%20panchayats%20extended%20full%20support%20to%20the%20wrestlers%20and%20organised%20their%20own%20protests.%20Women%20from%20the%20mahapanchayat%20rushed%20to%20Delhi%20to%20join%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20dharna.%20None%20of%20this%20moved%20Modi%20who%2C%20as%20a%20diehard%20despot%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewent%20by%20his%20own%20cold%20calculations.%20Jat%20votes%2C%20which%20can%20influence%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20spread%20over%20four%20states%2C%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbjp-jat-community-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-lok-sabha-seats-8655513%2F%5C%22%3Eimportant%20for%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20ignoring%20the%20Bri