ation.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20stony%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20now%20ongoing%20for%20over%20two%20months%2C%20belongs%20to%20a%20third%20category.%20The%20ethnic%20clashes%20which%20began%20on%20May%203%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fafter-lull-of-16-days-two-killed-in-manipur-as-rioters-fire-at-army%2Farticle67024263.ece%5C%22%3Ehave%20forced%3C%2Fa%3E%2037%2C000%20people%20into%20relief%20camps%2C%2012%2C000%20people%20to%20flee%20and%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20142.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%2036%2C000%20central%20forces%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECaught%20in%20a%20cleft%20stick%20of%20its%20own%20creation%2C%20any%20solution%20the%20government%20suggests%20could%20bounce%20back%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAuthoritarians%20the%20world%20over%20avoid%20such%20risks.%20They%20always%20seek%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20positive%20achievements%20and%20carefully%20avoid%20unpopular%20decisions.%20Hence%2C%20Modi%20deputed%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20latter%20drew%20a%20blank.%20This%20explains%20his%20refusal%20even%20to%20meet%20an%20opposition%20delegation%20to%20discuss%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20for%2010%20days.%20Finally%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwe-are-not-beggars-opposition-delegation-on-pm-modi-not-granting-a-meeting-on-manipur-crisis%2F1634396%2F%5C%22%3Eleft%20a%20memorandum%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPMO.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20delegations%20from%20Manipur%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-narendra-modi-silence-mlas-teams%5C%22%3Esimilar%20experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAngry%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%2C%20the%20protesters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fvideo%2Fprotesters-refuse-to-listen-to-pm-modi-saying-no-to-mann-ki-baat-yes-to-manipur-ki-baat-600203-2023-06-18%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20listen%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20homilies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clashes%20have%20forced%20even%20the%20RSS%20to%20make%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forganiser.org%2F2023%2F06%2F18%2F179608%2Frss-news%2Fmanipur-violence-rss-appeals-for-peace-says-no-place-for-hatred-in-democratic-setup%2F%5C%22%3Eformal%20appeal%20for%20peace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20not%20India%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20how%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%20handled%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20July%202001.%20He%20took%20an%20all-party%20delegation%20to%20Manipur%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepaper.telegraphindia.com%2Fimageview%2F437057%2F17364140%2Fundefined.html%5C%22%3Eheld%20two%20all-party%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20should%20be%20the%20practice%20in%20a%20democracy.%20Discussion%20at%20the%20National%20Integration%20Council%20was%20another%20tradition%20during%20the%20pre-Modi%20era.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESidestepping%20uncomfortable%20truths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESilence%20as%20a%20device%20to%20sidestep%20uncomfortable%20truths%20has%20been%20spreading%20to%20new%20areas.%20The%20PM%20persistently%20avoids%20talking%20about%20the%20ingress%20of%20Chinese%20troops%20at%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20ever%20since%20his%202020%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efaux%20pas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20had%20surprised%20everyone%20by%20claiming%20that%20%E2%80%9Cneither%20has%20anyone%20intruded%20into%2