jul%2F07%2Fmanipur-violence-escaped-covid-gotbeheaded-back-home-2592211.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Thiek%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Protestors%20shouted%20and%20yelled%20in%20anger%20as%20they%20showed%20their%20solidarity%20with%20their%20fellow%20tribesmen%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state.%20Effigies%20of%20state%20leaders%20were%20also%20lit%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20collective%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopularly%20known%20as%20ZORO%2C%20the%20organisation%20had%20earlier%20organised%20a%20rally%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20May%2C%20where%20they%20passed%20several%20resolutions%20including%20measures%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20re-unification%20of%20ethnic%20Zo%20tribes%20to%20bring%20them%20under%20one%20administrative%20setup%20through%20peaceful%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20three%20resolutions%20were%20adopted%20during%20the%20rally.%20One%20resolution%20was%20that%20ZORO%20stands%20in%20solidarity%20with%20their%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20Manipur%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20properties%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20their%20fight%20for%20survival%20and%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20was%20to%20make%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20Government%20to%20give%20the%20Zo%20ethnic%20people%20in%20Manipur%20a%20separate%20administration.%20Its%20third%20resolution%20was%20to%20work%20towards%20the%20unity%20of%20Zo%20ethnic%20people%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20rally%2C%20ZORO%20president%20R.%20Sangkawia%20highlighted%20various%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20were%20allegedly%20neglected%20by%20the%20state%20leaders%20in%20Manipur%20and%20questioned%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20central%20government%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDoes%20India%20consider%20the%20Zo%20people%20as%20foreigners%20that%20it%20has%20neglected%20us%20to%20this%20extent%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERini%20Ralte%2C%20secr