ther%20today%20as%20ZORO%20in%20Aizawl%20to%20be%20in%20solidarity%20with%20our%20suffering%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERalter%20said%20that%20they%20are%20only%20demanding%20their%20due%20right%20to%20have%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Meitei%20community%20do%20not%20want%20the%20tribals%20anymore.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20point%20of%20coming%20together%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20anymore%3F%20This%20is%20the%20only%20option%20they%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ralte%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20marked%20with%20a%20tape%20on%20his%20lips%20to%20display%20his%20alleged%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20as%20the%20ZORO%20condemned%20the%20silence%20over%20the%20issue.%20The%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20given%20the%20title%20%E2%80%9CMafia%20Godfather%E2%80%9D.%20An%20official%20said%20that%20the%20burning%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20was%20a%20display%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20deserves%20to%20die%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20effigy%20lit%20up%2C%20the%20crowd%20went%20into%20a%20fury%20shouting%20curses%20in%20Manipuri%20language%20against%20the%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20burning%20effigies%2C%20a%20mass%20prayer%20was%20conducted%20where%20all%20the%20people%20who%20gathered%2C%20shouted%20and%20cried%20in%20unison%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20Amid%20a%20solemn%20atmosphere%2C%20a%20mourning%20session%20commenced%2C%20with%20the%20ringing%20of%20a%20gong%2C%20evoking%20ancient%20traditions%20and%20conveying%20messages%20of%20sorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20protestors%20were%20displaced%20residents%20of%20Manipur.%20Among%20them%20was%20a%20college%20student%20Lalremruat%20Tonsing%20from%20Lamka%2C%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20gather%20here%20to%20show%20our%20solidarity%20in%20remembrance%20of%20our%20fathers%2C%20our%20brothers%2C%20our%20sisters%2C%20our%20mothers%20who%20are%20fighting%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20their%20lives%20to%20protect%20our%20lands%2C%20our%20rights%20and%20to%20protect%20our%20god-given%20tribal%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EEastMojo%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20said%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20take%20shelter%20in%20Aizawl%20because%20the%20education%20system%20back%20in%20Manipur%20had%20collapsed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20no%20longer%20go%20to%20college%2C%20and%20we%20are%20only%20left%20with%20the%20choice%20of%20getting%20out%20of%20town%20and%20starting%20a%20future%20here%20so%20that%20we%20can%20get%20education%20to%20build%20our%20land%20and%20our%20administration.%20We%20are%20left%20with%20no%20choice.%20Our%20brothers%20and%20our%20sisters%20are%20fighting%20there%20in%20Lamka.%20Every%20second%20of%20our%20life%20here%20is%20used%20up%20in%20our%20thoughts%20of%20them%20and%20today%2C%20the%20least%20we%20can%20do%20is%20to%20gather%20here%2C%20holding%20up%20placards%20and%20shouting%20for%20our%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tonsing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20shared%20by%20ZORO%2C%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20Manipur%20tolled%20over%20124%2C%20with%20over%20377%2C%20and%2060%20missing.%20The%20number%20of%20villages%20burnt%2C%20as%20per%20the%20tribal%20body%2C%20accounted%20for%20290%2C%20with%207%2C247%20houses%20burnt%2C%20357%20churches%20and%20quarters%20burnt%2C%20and%20about%2041%2C425%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eastmojo.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F07%2F12%2Fmizoram-zo-tribal-protestors-burn-effigies-of-pm-manipur-cm%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eastmojo.com%2F%5C%22%3EEastMojo%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689181093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID