s%20of%20a%20meeting%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20foreign%20ministers%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fthai-foreign-minister-says-he-met-with-myanmars-jailed-leader-suu-kyi-2023-07-12%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sought%20to%20underline%20that%20the%20objective%20of%20meeting%20Suu%20Kyi%20was%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Association%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20(ASEAN)%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20achieve%20peace%20in%20the%20conflict-ridden%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20meeting%2C%20Kanchana%20Patarachoke%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Thailand%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20said%20was%20held%20on%20Sunday%20and%20lasted%20over%20an%20hour.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20in%20good%20health%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%20(Pramudwinai)%20briefed%20ASEAN%20on%20the%20retreat%20this%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanchana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20access%20granted%20to%20the%20Thai%20foreign%20minister%20to%20meet%20Suu%20Kyi%20by%20the%20junta%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20given%20that%20the%20same%20requests%20from%20ASEAN%20and%20UN%20envoys%20were%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20military%20regime.%20While%20ASEAN%20member%20states%20have%20been%20opposed%20to%20engaging%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20junta%20for%20finding%20a%20political%20solution%20to%20the%20crisis%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20current%20Thailand%20government%20has%20been%20in%20its%20favour.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20meeting%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20Thailand%20government%E2%80%99s%20renewed%20push%20to%20make%20the%20junta%20part%20of%20talks%20given%20that%20it%20came%20just%20days%20before%20ASEAN%20foreign%20ministers%20meet%20in%20Jakarta%2C%20where%20Myanmar%20is%20expected%20to%20figure%20prominently.%20The%20meeting%20of%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20bloc%20is%20currently%20underway%20in%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%E2%80%99s%20government-in-exile%2C%20