%3A%22While%20access%20was%20granted%20to%20Don%20Pramudwinai%20to%20meet%20the%20deposed%20leader%2C%20similar%20requests%20from%20ASEAN%20and%20UN%20envoys%20were%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20military%20regime%20in%20the%20past.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fasean-leaders-myanmar-thai-foreign-ministersuu-kyi-meet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amnesty%20%E2%80%98Alarmed%E2%80%99%20at%20Manipur%20Violence%2C%20Asks%20Govt%20To%20Work%20With%20All%20Ethnic%20Groups%20To%20Restore%20Peace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12081122%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.08.47-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Amnesty%20International%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2012%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3Ealarmed%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinability%20of%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20protect%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D%2C%20asking%20the%20government%20to%20work%20with%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20community%20members%20of%20all%20ethnic%20groups%20to%20ensure%20that%20peace%20is%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20rights%20NGO%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ereleased%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Fasa20%2F6969%2F2023%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublic%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0expressing%20its%20concern%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20includes%20statements%20from%20victims%20of%20the%20violence%20and%20highlights%20India%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20international%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETitled%20%E2%80%9CIndia%3A%20Wanton%20killings%2C%20violence%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20statement%20i