20According%20to%20fact-finding%20teams%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20team%20of%20reporters%2C%20which%20visited%20the%20state%2C%20over%2060%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20survivor%20of%20the%20violence%20told%20the%20NGO%20that%20they%20and%20their%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20food%20or%20drinking%20water%20for%20two%20days%20at%20a%20relief%20camp%20and%20that%20their%20accommodation%20was%20%E2%80%9Cbasically%20a%20shed%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20%E2%80%9Cfacilities%20%5Bthat%20were%5D%20not%20hygienic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20gives%20a%20large%20berth%20to%20discussing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-high-court-internet%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eongoing%20internet%20shutdown%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20place%20for%20over%20two%20months%20now.%20In%20the%20following%20text%2C%20it%20highlights%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20international%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20judgement%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20are%20antithetical%20to%20the%20shutdown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CStates%20parties%20must%20not%20block%20or%20hinder%20internet%20connectivity%20to%20curb%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20which%20is%20a%20right%20enshrined%20in%C2%A0%20the%20International%20Covenant%20on%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%2C%20to%20which%20India%20is%20a%20state%20party%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20restrictions%20on%20the%20operation%20of%20information%20dissemination%20systems%20must%20conform%20with%20the%20tests%20for%20restrictions%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%E2%80%94notably%2C%20they%20should%20be%20legal%2C%20necessary%2C%20and%20proportionate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20tests%20are%20laid%20down%20under%20international%20human%20rights%20law%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20judgement%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalfreedomofexpression.columbia.edu%2Fcases%2Fbhasin-v-union-of-india%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAnuradha%20Bhasin%20vs.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20noted%20that%20the%20degree%20and%20scope%20of%20internet%20restrictions%20had%20to%20be%20proportionate%E2%80%9D.%20.%20Blanket%20%E2%80%93%20or%20total%20%E2%80%93%20cuts%20to%20internet%20access%20(or%20internet%20shutdowns)%20are%20inherently%20disproportionate%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20notes%20India%E2%80%99s%20status%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findia-remains-internet-shutdown-capital-of-the-world-for-fifth-year-running-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eglobal%20leader%20in%20internet%20shutdowns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20asked%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20immediately%20restore%20internet%20access%20in%20the%20state%20and%20work%20with%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20community%20members%20of%20all%20ethnic%20groups%20to%20ensure%20that%20peace%20and%20security%20are%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVictims%20of%20violence%20have%20a%20right%20to%20truth%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20justice.%20Police%20excesses%20and%20reports%20of%20police%20bias%20need%20to%20be%20immediately%2C%20independently%2C%20and%20impartially%20investigated.%20Indian%20state%20authorities%20should%20coordinate%20with%20each%20other%20and%20with%20local%20groups%20to%20ensure%20that%20necessities%20of%20adequate%20and%20sanitary%20housing%2C%20safety%2C%20clothing%2C%20clean%20water%2C%20nutrition%20and%20health%20care%20is%20accessible%20to%20all%20%5Binternally%20displaced%20persons%5D%20who%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20flee.%20Authorities%20must%20facilitate%20the%20IDPs%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20voluntarily%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20rebuild%20their%20lives%20by%20ensuring%20safe%20rehabilitation%20and%2For%20resettlement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amnesty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGO%20has%20also%20been%20targeted%20by%20Indian%20authorities.%20Its%20Bangalore%20and%20Delhi%20offices%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famnesty-india-cbi-raids-fcra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraided%20by%20the%20CBI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202019%20and%20it%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famnesty-international-india-shuts-down-inquiries-investigating-agencies-ed-cbi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eforced%20to%20shut%20down%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20India%20operations%20in%202020%20after%20its%20accounts%20were%20frozen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20a%20federal%20financial%20crimes%20agency%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fenforcement-directorate-amnesty-india-money-laundering%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efiled%20a%20money%20laundering%20chargesheet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20its%20India%20division%20last%20year%20and%20fined%20it%20Rs%2051%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689176712000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F12081122%2FScreenshot-2023-06-12-at-8.08.47-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famnesty-alarm-manipur-violence-peace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20human%20rights%20NGO%20released%20a%20public%20statement%20in%20which%20it%20takes%20note%20of%20reprisals%20against%20scholars%20and%20activists%20and%20allegations%20of%20police%20excesses.%20The%20statement%20also%20features%20conversations%20with%20victims%20of%20Manipur's%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famnesty-alarm-manipur-violence-peace%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Milan%20Kundera%2C%20author%20of%20'The%20Unbearable%20Lightness%20of%20Being'%2C%20dies%20at%2094%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689175200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101705093%2Cimgsize-26838.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmilan-kundera-author-of-the-unbearable-lightness-of-being-dies-at-94%2Farticleshow%2F101705095.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101705095.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%20Czech-born%20writer%20Milan%20Kundera%2C%20author%20of%20the%20novel%20%26quot%3BThe%20Unbearable%20Lightness%20of%20Being%26quot%3B%20who%20lived%20nearly%20five%20decades%20in%20Paris%20after%20emigrating%20in%20disillusionment%20from%20his%20Communist-ruled%20homeland%2C%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2094.The%20Moravian%20Library%20(MZK)%20in%20the%20Czech%20city%20of%20Brno%2C%20which%20houses%20Kundera's%20personal%20collection%2C%20said%20he%20died%20in%20his%20Paris%20apartment%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20long%20illness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmilan-kundera-author-of-the-unbearable-lightness-of-being-dies-at-94%2Farticleshow%2F101705095.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmilan-kundera-author-of-the-unbearable-lightness-of-being-dies-at-94%2Famp_articleshow%2F101705095.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmilan-kundera-author-of-the-unbearable-lightness-of-being-dies-at-94%2Famp_articleshow%2F101705095.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Farming%20Starts%20in%20Manipur%20Amid%20Tight%20Security%2C%20Protesters%20Decry%20Deployment%20of%20Central%20Forces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01132506%2FAgriculture_main.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Agricultural%20activities%20have%20reportedly%20started%20in%20some%20vulnerable%20areas%20of%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%20with%20security%20cover%20provided%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20and%20central%20forces%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-security-arrangement-for-farmers-draws-backlash%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20people%20have%20protested%20against%20the%20deployment%20of%20central%20forces%20in%20the%20farming%20areas%2C%20said%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-security-arrangement-for-farmers-draws-backlash%5C%22%3Ereport.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%208%2C%20I.K.%20Muivah%2C%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20(Ops)%2C%20had%20told%20the%20news%20outlet%20about%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20deployment%20of%202%2C267%20personnel%20from%20Manipur%20Rifles%20and%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20said%20that%20for%20the%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20822%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%3B%20298%20personnel%20for%20Imphal%20East%3B%20236%20personnel%20for%20Bishnupur%3B%20147%20personnel%20for%20Thoubal%3B%20204%20personnel%20for%20Kakching%3B%20200%20personnel%20for%20Kangpokpi%20and%20300%20personnel%20for%20Churachandpur%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20informed%20that%20while%20conducting%20search%20operations%2C%20the%20state%20police%20and%20central%20forces%20destroyed%20two%20more%20bunkers%2C%20and%20recovered%20six%20more%20arms%20from%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-gun-licenses-biren-singh-violence%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20In%20Past%207%20Years%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20Govt%20Has%20Issued%20Highest%20Number%20of%20Gun%20Licences%20in%20Northeast%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20informed%20that%20about%20127%20nakas%2Fcheckpoints%20were%20installed%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20Manipur%2C%20both%20in%20the%20hill%20and%20the%20valley.%20It%20added%20that%20298%20persons%20were%20detained%20in%20connection%20with%20violations%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hundreds%20of%20women%20of%20Koirengei%20Awang%20village%20area%20on%20July%2011%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20authorities%20for%20sending%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20personnel%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20farmers%20during%20agricultural%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20personnel%20have%20been%20sent%20in%20Tingri%2C%20Khongnangpokpi%2C%20Chirik%20Loitong%20and%20Mapao%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesters%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-security-arrangement-for-farmers-draws-backlash%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20during%20a%20recent%20public%20meeting%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20disallow%20any%20central%20forces%2C%20and%20allow%20only%20state%20forces%2C%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20farmers%20and%20paddy%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumerous%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20who%20went%20to%20the%20fields%20for%20farming%20activities%20