0hotel%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20the%20market.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20unorganised%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20professional%20players%20other%20than%20our%20neighbourhood%20%3Cem%3Edhobis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RedSeer%E2%80%99s%20research%20report%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Laundry%20Services%20Market%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20laundry%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20to%20%2415%20billion%20by%202025%E2%80%9D.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20is%20less%20than%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20organise%20the%20laundry%20industry%20and%20offer%20%E2%80%98quality%20and%20consistent%20services%E2%80%99.%20Arunabh%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20August%202016%2C%20and%20they%20launched%20a%20laundromat%20service%20called%20UClean%20in%20January%202017%20with%20a%20capital%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20business%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20microentrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20uclean%20store%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2