ng%20job%20to%20%E2%80%98wash%20people%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20linen%E2%80%99.%20Despite%20having%20run%20a%20successful%20startup%20called%20Franglobal%2C%20he%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20at%20a%20very%20well-paying%20job%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20chase%20this%20idea.%20My%20family%20was%20scandalised%20that%20I%20was%20quitting%20my%20job%20to%20%E2%80%98become%20a%20%3Cem%3Edhobi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20Even%20when%20we%20started%20looking%20for%20investors%2C%20while%20they%20were%20happy%20with%20the%20idea%2C%20no%20one%20was%20willing%20to%20be%20the%20first%20one%20to%20invest.%20We%20were%20rejected%20by%20almost%2050%20investors%20in%20the%20first%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20able%20to%20convince%20a%20dry%20cleaner%20to%20invest%20and%20open%20the%20first%20two%20stores%20of%20UClean.%20It%20took%20them%20100%20days%20to%20find%20an%20investor.%20Though%20Arunabh%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20August%202016%2C%20the%20first%20store%20was%20opened%20in%20January%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20What%20started%20with%20a%20seed%20capital%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20has%20a%20turnover%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322111%2Fdelhi-arpit-raj-starts-tea-franchise-chaai-seth-college-tapri-to-crore-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERs%20100%20crore%20today.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20is%20to%20build%20the%20laundry%20industry%20of%20India.%20We%20are%20also%20creating%20a%20lot%20of%20micro-entrepreneurs%20along%20the%20way.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20present%20in%20all%20neighbourhoods%20by%202028%20and%20open%206000%2B%20outlets%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20We%20also%20plan%20to%20expand%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20(MENA)%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5