ives%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20where%20our%20food%20comes%20from%20and%20the%20hard%20work%20involved%20in%20growing%20food.%20I%20love%20how%20our%20teachers%20always%20give%20us%20the%20time%20to%20explore%20the%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Akanksha%20and%20Saurabh%20believe%20that%20the%20school%20takes%20a%20step%20forward%20while%20going%20back%20to%20the%20roots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20nature%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20if%20given%20the%20opportunity%20the%20students%20will%20feel%20inspired%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F84622%2Fsubbaiah-bharathidasan-arulagam-saving-vultures-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreserve%20and%20protect%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20kids%20of%20the%20upcoming%20generation%20lack%20a%20connection%20with%20the%20wild%20and%20the%20school%20helps%20to%20forge%20that%20connection%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saurabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688733767000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Built%20by%20architects%20Saurabh%20Gupta%20and%20Akanksha%20Gupta%2C%20the%20EuroSchool%20near%20Bannerghatta%20National%20Park%20in%20Bengaluru%20imbibes%20sustainability%20at%20its%20core%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20impart%20learning%20immersed%20in%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323054%2Fbengaluru-architects-build-zero-waste-sustainable-euroschool-near-national-park%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20'Game-Changing'%20Technology%20Th