o%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhijit%20explains%20that%20greywater%20comprises%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20highlighting%20the%20limitations%20of%20greywater%20recycling%20systems%2C%20Abhijit%20says%20that%20space%20is%20a%20major%20constraint.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20we%20have%20to%20check%20where%20we%20can%20set%20up%20the%20tank%20to%20collect%20greywater.%20Generally%2C%20we%20set%20it%20up%20underground%20and%20in%20a%20basement.%20We%20get%20many%20queries%20from%20individual%20flat%20owners%2C%20but%20we%20can%20set%20up%20such%20a%20system%20for%20an%20entire%20building%2C%20as%20it%20would%20not%20be%20cost-effective%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20residential%20complexes%2C%20Abhijit%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20system%20into%20restaurants%2C%20institutes%2C%20canteens%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20are%20totally%20dependent%20on%20the%20monsoon%20every%20year%2C%20which%20has%20not%20failed%20us.%20But%20with%20changing%20weather%20patterns%20amid%20climate%20change%2C%20we%20are%20to%20get%20below%20average%20monsoon%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Our%20water%20resource%20is%20limited%20but%20our%20con